const title = "BP | MineralWise";
const description = "BP is a multinational oil company with headquarters in London, United Kingdom. BP stock is listed on the NYSE under the symbol BP. BP was founded in 1909 as the Anglo-Persian Oil Company by William Knox D";

const content = "<div id=\"mm-0\">\n    <section id=\"sObP6GwHMOZd_sObP6GwHMOZd\"><div><div><div id=\"\"><div><div><p>BP</p></div></div></div><div><div><div><div><div id=\"\"><div><div><p></p><p>BP is a multinational oil company with headquarters in London, United Kingdom. BP stock is listed on the NYSE under the symbol BP. BP was founded in 1909 as the Anglo-Persian Oil Company by William Knox D'Arcy.&nbsp;BP currently has exploration and production undertakings in 30 countries, and operates 16 refineries with a combined output of 2.3 million barrels of oil per day.</p><p><br></p><h2><strong>Contact Information for Royalty Owners - Tel. (800) 732-6626</strong></h2><p>Those who own gas royalties and oil royalties are an important group to BP. If you receive oil royalty or gas royalty from a lease under production by BP, you can contact them at (800) 732-6626.</p><p><br></p><h2><strong>BP Production Volume Verification</strong></h2><p>If you are a lease holder (lessor) currently under production by BP, you can verify your oil and gas production volumes by visiting <a href=\"https://www.mineralwise.com/owners-guide/leased-and-producing/oil-and-gas-production-volume-verification\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">How to Verify Your Oil and Gas Production Volumes</a>. This page includes links to the state agencies that record oil and gas production data and also covers the basics of how oil and gas is measured.</p><p></p></div></div></div></div></div><div><div><div id=\"\"><div><picture><source srcset=\"/images/BP.jpg, /images/BP.jpg\" media=\"(min-width: 992px)\"><source srcset=\"/images/BP.jpg, /images/BP.jpg\" media=\"(min-width: 768px)\"><img srcset=\"/images/BP.jpg, /images/BP.jpg\" src=\"/images/BP.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" title=\"BP.jpg\" draggable=\"false\"></picture></div></div></div></div></div></div><div id=\"\"><div><div data-brz-translate-text=\"1\"><p data-generated-css=\"brz-css-c1lJY\" data-uniq-id=\"f2pnu\"><a style=\"color: rgba(var